TITLE: Swapping or Filling Option in Sui Move
DESCRIPTION: Swaps the old value inside the option with a new value and returns the old value, or fills it if there is no old value. Allows for the option not holding a value.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/crates/sui-framework/docs/std/option.md#2025-04-22_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: Move
CODE:
```
public fun swap_or_fill<Element>(t: &mut Option<Element>, e: Element): Option<Element> {
    let vec_ref = &mut t.vec;
    let old_value = if (vec_ref.is_empty()) none() else some(vec_ref.pop_back());
    vec_ref.push_back(e);
    old_value
}
```

