TITLE: DeepBook Pool Structure Implementation in Move
DESCRIPTION: Core Pool structure definition for DeepBook trading pairs, implementing order management using crit-bit trees. The structure maintains bid/ask orders, user open orders, fee rates, and asset custodians for a specific trading pair.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/docs/content/standards/deepbookv2/pools.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: move
