TITLE: Requesting to Add Stake to a Validator
DESCRIPTION: This function handles a request to add stake to a validator's staking pool. It processes the stake, updates the next epoch stake, and emits a StakingRequestEvent.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/crates/sui-framework/docs/sui_system/validator.md#2025-04-22_snippet_31

