TITLE: Implementing divide_u64 Function
DESCRIPTION: Divides a u64 integer by a fixed-point number, handling division by zero checks and proper scaling of the result.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/crates/sui-framework/docs/std/fixed_point32.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: move
CODE:
```
public fun divide_u64(val: u64, divisor: FixedPoint32): u64 {
    assert!(divisor.value != 0, EDIVISION_BY_ZERO);
    let scaled_value = val as u128 << 32;
    let quotient = scaled_value / (divisor.value as u128);
    assert!(quotient <= MAX_U64, EDIVISION);
    quotient as u64
}
```

