TITLE: Extracting UpdateBridgeLimit Message in Rust
DESCRIPTION: Extracts an UpdateBridgeLimit message from a BridgeMessage. It parses the payload, validates the chain ID, and constructs an UpdateBridgeLimit struct.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/crates/sui-framework/docs/bridge/message.md#2025-04-22_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: Rust
CODE:
```
public fun extract_update_bridge_limit(message: &BridgeMessage): UpdateBridgeLimit {
    let mut bcs = bcs::new(message.payload);
    let sending_chain = bcs.peel_u8();
    let limit = peel_u64_be(&mut bcs);
    chain_ids::assert_valid_chain_id(sending_chain);
    assert!(bcs.into_remainder_bytes().is_empty(), ETrailingBytes);
    UpdateBridgeLimit {
        receiving_chain: message.source_chain,
        sending_chain,
        limit
    }
}
```

