TITLE: Creating New Tic-Tac-Toe Game Object in Move
DESCRIPTION: This Move function (`new`) creates a new Tic-Tac-Toe game object on the Sui blockchain. It initializes the game with parameters such as size, players, and initial game state and uses the Sui framework to generate a unique ID (UID) for the game, resulting in a new NFT at a specific address.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/docs/content/concepts/gaming.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: Move
