TITLE: Searching for Element in Vector in Move
DESCRIPTION: This function checks if a given element exists in the vector. It returns true if the element is found, false otherwise.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/crates/sui-framework/docs/std/vector.md#2025-04-22_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: Move
CODE:
```
public fun contains<Element>(v: &vector<Element>, e: &Element): bool {
    let mut i = 0;
    let len = v.length();
    while (i < len) {
        if (&v[i] == e) return true;
        i = i + 1;
    };
    false
}
```

