TITLE: Implementing a Sum Function with While Loop in Move
DESCRIPTION: A function that calculates the sum of numbers from 1 to n using a while loop. The function iterates through each number, adding it to a running sum until the counter exceeds n.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/external-crates/move/documentation/book/src/control-flow/loops.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: move
CODE:
```
fun sum(n: u64): u64 {
    let mut sum = 0;
    let mut i = 1;
    while (i <= n) {
        sum = sum + i;
        i = i + 1
    };

    sum
}
