TITLE: Updating Global Randomness State in Sui
DESCRIPTION: This function updates the global randomness state stored in the Random object. It can only be called by the system address during epoch changes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/crates/sui-framework/docs/sui/random.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: Move
CODE:
```
public fun update_randomness_state(
    self: &mut Random,
    new_randomness: vector<u8>,
    ctx: &TxContext,
) {
    assert!(ctx.sender() == @0x0, ENotSystemAddress);
    let inner = load_inner_mut(self);
    let new_epoch = ctx.epoch();
    assert!(
        new_epoch > inner.epoch || 
        (new_epoch == inner.epoch && ctx.epoch_timestamp_ms() == 0),
        EInvalidRandomnessUpdate
    );
    inner.epoch = new_epoch;
    inner.randomness_round = 0;
    inner.random_bytes = new_randomness;
}
```

