TITLE: Implementing a Sum Function with Loop Expression in Move
DESCRIPTION: A function that calculates the sum of numbers from 1 to n using a loop expression with a break condition. The loop continues until i exceeds n.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/external-crates/move/documentation/book/src/control-flow/loops.md#2025-04-22_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: move
CODE:
```
fun sum(n: u64): u64 {
    let mut sum = 0;
    let mut i = 1;

    loop {
       i = i + 1;
       if (i >= n) break;
       sum = sum + i;
    };

    sum
}
```

