SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/crates/sui-framework/docs/std/option.md#2025-04-22_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: Move
CODE:
```
public fun swap<Element>(t: &mut Option<Element>, e: Element): Element {
    assert!(t.is_some(), EOPTION_NOT_SET);
    let vec_ref = &mut t.vec;
    let old_value = vec_ref.pop_back();
    vec_ref.push_back(e);
    old_value
}
```

