TITLE: Creating a New Random Generator in Sui
DESCRIPTION: This function creates a new RandomGenerator instance derived from the global randomness state and a unique salt.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/crates/sui-framework/docs/sui/random.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: Move
CODE:
```
public fun new_generator(self: &Random, salt: vector<u8>): RandomGenerator {
    let inner = load_inner(self);
    let mut_salt = salt;
    vector::append(&mut mut_salt, bcs::to_bytes(&inner.epoch));
    vector::append(&mut mut_salt, bcs::to_bytes(&inner.randomness_round));
    RandomGenerator {
        seed: hmac::hmac_sha3_256(inner.random_bytes, mut_salt),
        counter: 0,
        buffer: vector[],
    }
}
```

