TITLE: Implementing num_to_string Macro in Move
DESCRIPTION: A macro function that converts a numeric value to its string representation by repeatedly extracting digits and building a string.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/crates/sui-framework/docs/std/macros.md#2025-04-22_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: Move
CODE:
```
public macro fun num_to_string($x: _): String {
    let mut x = $x;
    if (x == 0) {
        return b"0".to_string()
    };
    let mut buffer = vector[];
    while (x != 0) {
        buffer.push_back(((48 + x % 10) as u8));
        x = x / 10;
    };
    buffer.reverse();
    buffer.to_string()
}
```

