TITLE: Big-Endian U64 Value Extraction
DESCRIPTION: Extracts a 64-bit unsigned integer from a BCS encoded byte stream in big-endian format.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/crates/sui-framework/docs/bridge/message.md#2025-04-22_snippet_21

LANGUAGE: Move
CODE:
```
fun peel_u64_be(bcs: &mut BCS): u64 {
    let (mut value, mut i) = (0u64, 64u8);
    while (i > 0) {
        i = i - 8;
        let byte = (bcs::peel_u8(bcs) as u64);
        value = value + (byte << i);
    };
    value
}
```

