TITLE: Defining zip_map_ref Macro for Vector Element Transformation with References
DESCRIPTION: This macro applies a function to pairs of referenced elements from two given vectors, collecting the results into a new vector. It ensures that the input vectors are of the same length, aborting if they are not, and maintains the order of the elements.
