TITLE: Implementing multiply_u64 Function
DESCRIPTION: Multiplies a u64 integer by a fixed-point number, handling overflow checks and proper scaling of the result.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/crates/sui-framework/docs/std/fixed_point32.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: move
CODE:
```
public fun multiply_u64(val: u64, multiplier: FixedPoint32): u64 {
    let unscaled_product = val as u128 * (multiplier.value as u128);
    let product = unscaled_product >> 32;
    assert!(product <= MAX_U64, EMULTIPLICATION);
    product as u64
}
```

