TITLE: Add Dynamic Object Field Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Macro implementing the core logic for adding a dynamic object field, including key wrapping and child object linking.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/crates/sui-framework/docs/sui/dynamic_object_field.md#2025-04-22_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: Move
CODE:
```
macro fun add_impl<$Name: copy + drop + store, $Value: key>(
    $object: &mut UID,
    $name: $Name,
    $value: $Value,
) {
    let object = $object;
    let name = $name;
    let value = $value;
    let key = Wrapper { name };
    let id = object::id(&value);
    field::add(object, key, id);
    let (field, _) = field::field_info<Wrapper<$Name>>(object, key);
    add_child_object(field.to_address(), value);
}
```

