TITLE: Implementing Remove for Dynamic Object Fields in Move
DESCRIPTION: This macro function implements removing a dynamic object field. It takes a mutable reference to an object UID and a name, removes the field, and returns the value of the specified type.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/crates/sui-framework/docs/sui/dynamic_object_field.md#2025-04-22_snippet_15

LANGUAGE: Move
CODE:
```
macro fun remove_impl<$Name: copy + drop + store, $Value: key>(
    $object: &mut UID,
    $name: $Name,
): $Value {
    let object = $object;
    let name = $name;
    let key = Wrapper { name };
    let (field, value_id) = field::field_info<Wrapper<$Name>>(object, key);
    let value = remove_child_object<$Value>(field.to_address(), value_id);
    field::remove<Wrapper<$Name>, ID>(object, key);
    value
}
```

