TITLE: Extracting Substring in Move
DESCRIPTION: Returns a substring using given byte indices. The indices must be at valid UTF-8 character boundaries to ensure the result is valid UTF-8.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/external-crates/move/crates/move-stdlib/docs/std/string.md#2025-04-22_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: Move
CODE:
```
public fun substring(s: &String, i: u64, j: u64): String {
    let bytes = &s.bytes;
    let l = bytes.length();
    assert!(
        j <= l &&
            i <= j &&
            internal_is_char_boundary(bytes, i) &&
            internal_is_char_boundary(bytes, j),
        EInvalidIndex,
    );
    String { bytes: internal_sub_string(bytes, i, j) }
}
```

