LANGUAGE: Move
CODE:
```
public fun destroy_some<Element>(t: Option<Element>): Element {
    assert!(t.is_some(), EOPTION_NOT_SET);
    let Option { mut vec } = t;
    let elem = vec.pop_back();
    vec.destroy_empty();
    elem
}
```

