TITLE: Applying Function to Vector Elements by Reference in Rust
DESCRIPTION: This macro function performs an action on each element of a vector by reference, without modifying the vector itself.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/external-crates/move/crates/move-stdlib/docs/std/vector.md#2025-04-22_snippet_17

