SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/crates/sui-framework/docs/sui/kiosk.md#2025-04-22_snippet_22

LANGUAGE: Move
CODE:
```
public fun place_and_list<T: key + store>(
    self: &mut Kiosk,
    cap: &KioskOwnerCap,
    item: T,
    price: u64,
) {
    let id = object::id(&item);
    self.place(cap, item);
    self.list<T>(cap, id, price)
}
```

