TITLE: Loading Mutable Bridge Inner State in Move
DESCRIPTION: Loads and validates the inner state of the bridge with mutable access, ensuring version compatibility. Returns a mutable reference to BridgeInner.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/crates/sui-framework/docs/bridge/bridge.md#2025-04-22_snippet_20

LANGUAGE: Move
CODE:
```
fun load_inner_mut(bridge: &mut Bridge): &mut BridgeInner {
    let version = bridge.inner.version();
    assert!(version == CURRENT_VERSION, EWrongInnerVersion);
    let inner: &mut BridgeInner = bridge.inner.load_value_mut();
    assert!(inner.bridge_version == version, EWrongInnerVersion);
    inner
}
