TITLE: Updating Validator P2P Address for Next Epoch in Sui System
DESCRIPTION: Updates a validator's P2P address for the next epoch in the Sui system state. The change takes effect from the next epoch. Requires mutable access to SuiSystemState and the transaction context.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/crates/sui-framework/docs/sui_system/sui_system.md#2025-04-22_snippet_22

LANGUAGE: Move
