TITLE: Adding DEEP Price Point for Fee Discounts
DESCRIPTION: Function to add a DEEP price point to a pool, enabling the calculation of DEEP token fee discounts. This function needs to be called periodically (every 1-10 minutes) via a cron job for pools that want to offer DEEP token fee discounts.
