TITLE: Derive Reference Gas Price in Move
DESCRIPTION: Function to calculate reference gas price based on validator-submitted gas prices weighted by stake. Returns a gas price that satisfies 2/3 validator stake weighted consensus.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/crates/sui-framework/docs/sui_system/validator_set.md#2025-04-22_snippet_19

LANGUAGE: Move
CODE:
```
public fun derive_reference_gas_price(self: &ValidatorSet): u64 {
    let entries = self
        .active_validators
        .map_ref!(|v| pq::new_entry(v.gas_price(), v.voting_power()));
    let mut pq = pq::new(entries);
    let mut sum = 0;
    let threshold = voting_power::total_voting_power() - voting_power::quorum_threshold();
    let mut result = 0;
    while (sum < threshold) {
        let (gas_price, voting_power) = pq.pop_max();
        result = gas_price;
        sum = sum + voting_power;
    };
    result
}
```

