TITLE: Dividing Integer by UQ32_32 in Move
DESCRIPTION: Divides a u64 integer by a UQ32_32 fixed-point number, truncating any fractional part of the quotient. Aborts if the divisor is zero or if the quotient overflows.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/external-crates/move/crates/move-stdlib/docs/std/uq32_32.md#2025-04-22_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: Move
CODE:
```
public fun int_div(val: u64, divisor: UQ32_32): u64 {
    std::macros::uq_int_div!<u64, u128>(
        val,
        divisor.0,
        std::u64::max_value!(),
        FRACTIONAL_BITS,
        abort EDivisionByZero,
        abort EOverflow,
    )
}
```

