SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/external-crates/move/documentation/book/src/uses.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: move
CODE:
```
use std::vector;
use std::option as o;

fun new_vec(): vector<o::Option<u8>> {
    let mut v = vector[];
    vector::push_back(&mut v, o::some(0));
    vector::push_back(&mut v, o::none());
    v
}
```

