TITLE: Mapping Option<T> to Option<U> by Reference in Sui Move
DESCRIPTION: The 'map_ref' macro function maps an Option<T> to Option<U> by applying a function to a contained value by reference. The original Option<T> is preserved. It's similar to Rust's t.map(f). It takes a reference to an Option<T> and a closure as parameters, and returns an Option<U>.
