TITLE: Implementing Option and Macro in Move
DESCRIPTION: Macro that executes a closure on the value if Some, otherwise returns None. Equivalent to Rust's and_then() method.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/crates/sui-framework/docs/std/option.md#2025-04-22_snippet_23

LANGUAGE: move
CODE:
```
public macro fun and<$T, $U>($o: Option<$T>, $f: |$T| -> Option<$U>): Option<$U> {
    let o = $o;
    if (o.is_some()) {
        $f(o.destroy_some())
    } else {
        o.destroy_none();
        none()
    }
}
```

