TITLE: Finding Leftmost Leaf in CritbitTree Subtree (Move)
DESCRIPTION: Helper function to find the leftmost leaf in a subtree of the CritbitTree, starting from a given root node.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/crates/sui-framework/docs/deepbook/critbit.md#2025-04-22_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: Move
CODE:
```
fun left_most_leaf<V: store>(tree: &CritbitTree<V>, root: u64): u64 {
    let mut ptr = root;
    while (ptr < PARTITION_INDEX){
        ptr = table::borrow(& tree.internal_nodes, ptr).left_child;
    };
    ptr
}
```

