                                        	m/44'/784'/0'/0'/0' for ed25519 or m/54'/784'/0'/0/0 for secp256k1 or m/74'/784'/0'/0/0 for secp256r1. Word length can be { word12 |
                                        	word15 | word18 | word21 | word24} default to word12 if not specified
