TITLE: Becoming a Validator Candidate
DESCRIPTION: Command to submit an on-chain transaction to become a validator candidate.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/nre/validator_tool.md#2025-04-22_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
$SUI_BINARY validator become-candidate {path-to}validator.info
```

