TITLE: Building Sui Project without Linting
DESCRIPTION: Command to build a Sui project with linting disabled, which skips code style and quality checks to focus on compilation only.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/sui/blob/main/external-crates/move/crates/move-cli/tests/build_tests/lint_flags/args.txt#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
build --no-lint
```
